Title extraction from PowerPoint document.
We only consider extraction of the main title.
Next, we define a ‘specification" for human judgments in title data annotation.
A number of reasons can be considered.
The rules include a title is usually in consecutive lines in the same format , a document can have no title , titles in images are not considered , a title should not contain words like ‘draft '' , 147 ‘whitepaper '' , etc , if it is difficult to determine which is the title , select the one in the largest font size , and if 